text: Jackel, Jäckel or Jaeckel may refer to: * Karl Jäckel (1913–1984), German U-boat coxswain in World War II * Peter Jaeckel, also Peter Jäckel, mathematician, and finance academic and practitioner * Eberhard Jäckel (born 1929), German historian, noted for his studies of Hitler's role in German history *A German pet form for the given name Jakob, a cognate of Jacob and James in English
title: Jackel (disambiguation)
